column1: #  This file contains all of the measured fold-change values from flow cytometry
#  for a collection of biological replicates.
#   date: Date the experiment was conducted
#   username: Identifier of the user who collected the data
#   mutant: Identity of the LacI mutant
#   operator: Identifier of the native *lac* operator sequence
#   IPTGuM: Concentration of the inducer IPTG in micromolar
#   repressors: Mean number of repressors per cell (functional dimers)
#   fold_change: Mean fold-change in gene expression of all cells in that replicate
#   class: Identifier for the mutant class.
#          DBL -> Double mutants (one inducer binding mutant + DNA binding mutant)
